        "link": "https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_CZeHryfbX/?id=3441425086262408919_29666268335",
        "share_text": "Volcom presents\u00c2\u00a0\nHORSE\u00c2\u00a0\nA surf film by James Kates\u00c2\u00a0\nStarring Noa Deane in a striking\u00c2\u00a0vignette of travel and shelf discovery.\u00c2\u00a0\nAppearances from Tom Gillespie & Makoa Gomez.\u00c2\u00a0\nOriginal score by Russell W\n\nWhat better way to spend your Father\u00e2\u0080\u0099s Day!\n\n\u00f0\u009f\u009a\u00aaPub Open from 7am\n\u00f0\u009f\u008c\u00baLive Music* 2 - 4pm\n\u00f0\u009f\u00a5\u00a9Kitchen pumping 12 - 7pm\n\u00f0\u009f\u008e\u00acFilm plays at 7pm (Ticketed see link in bio)\n\nFathers Day Specials:\n\u00f0\u009f\u00a6\u0090\u00e2\u0080\u0098Surf n Turf\u00e2\u0080\u0099\n350g ribeye, garlic prawns $50 w/ a schooner of Young Henrys\n\n\u00f0\u009f\u00a5\u0083\u00e2\u0080\u0098Dad\u00e2\u0080\u0099s Boiler Maker\u00e2\u0080\u0099\nBuy your dad a Young Henrys Motorcycle Oil and get a free Boiler Maker upgrade (house shot)\n\n\u00f0\u009f\u008c\u00baThe band*:\nThe High Andies\nA Hawaiian Jazz Trio that will make you feel like you\u00e2\u0080\u0099re in the Pe\u00e2\u0080\u0099ahi/Jaws green room\u00e2\u0080\u00a6\n\nMinors can attend with a responsible parent or guardian.\n\nThe Oak Tighes Hill promotes the responsible service of alcohol, steaks, prawns and good times \u00f0\u009f\u00a4\u0099",
